);\n    }\n\n    @Override\n    Object invokeStaticMethod(final Method method, final Object... args) throws Exception {\n        return invokeStaticMethod.invoke(null, method, args);\n    }\n}"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1784160183662}}
